# New Frame - Cursor AI Rules

## Project Context
This is a UI project exported from UXMagic Copilot. The design has been converted to HTML/CSS.

## Coding Standards
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Follow modern CSS practices (Flexbox, Grid, Custom Properties)
- Maintain responsive design principles
- Keep accessibility in mind (ARIA labels, semantic structure)
- Use modern JavaScript ES6+ syntax

## File Structure
- index.html: Clean HTML file (no external CDN dependencies)
- styles.css: Self-contained CSS styles with proper structure
- script.js: Interactive features and utilities
- package.json: Project configuration and dependencies
- .cursorrules: AI assistant guidelines

## AI Assistant Guidelines
- Focus on clean, maintainable code
- Suggest improvements for accessibility and performance
- Help with responsive design enhancements
- Provide modern CSS solutions
- Assist with JavaScript interactivity if needed

## Design System
- Colors and typography are defined in the exported style guide
- Maintain consistent spacing and sizing
- Follow the established visual hierarchy
